            <img class="card-img-top team-image" src="https://oyster.ignimgs.com/mediawiki/apis.ign.com/pokemon-black-and-white/3/38/Pokemans_003.gif?width=1280" alt="Card image pokemon 4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Venusaur</h5>
                <p class="card-text">The plant blooms when it is absorbing solar energy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pokemon-5 card">
            <div class="dropdown">
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="add-pokemon" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Choose your pokemon</button>
            </div>
            <img class="card-img-top team-image" src="https://oyster.ignimgs.com/mediawiki/apis.ign.com/pokemon-black-and-white/b/b5/Pokemans_143.gif?width=1280" alt="Card image pokemon 5">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Snorlax</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotund bulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.</p>
