            </div>
            <img class="card-img-top team-image" src="https://oyster.ignimgs.com/mediawiki/apis.ign.com/pokemon-black-and-white/a/ac/Pokemans_131.gif?width=1280" alt="Card image pokemon 6">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Lapras</h5>
